# TASK::REMOVE_COVER_BLOCKING_AREAS_AT_POSITION

## Summary
Removes the specified cover area(s) added by ADD_COVER_BLOCKING_AREA. Will remove ALL blocking areas that intersect this point

## Parameters
* **FLOAT** positionX
* **FLOAT** positionY
* **FLOAT** positionZ
